reviewText: have seen Gabby n old westerns before he had a beard. Good quality
Great nostalgic look at classic westerns by one of our favorite and lovable western stars.  Each episode is a must-see.

Being a Gabby Hayes fan which therefore dates me, it reminds me of a local television host in the early days of TV who would sit on a rock with a painted Cactus background and show old westerns, whcih all the kids loved.  Well Gabby is the best and won him an emmy award nomination. Critics Choice has decent transfers for all three volumes if you can get them.

The sharpness of the pictures are less than I thought they would be.

  Jim
